column1: Results for the Arkansas Christmas Classic 11/21/09 Russellville Classic  We want to thank Terry Tucker and all the Top Hogs for putting on another great meet. Also want to thank Ambre Tarpley for coming up from Tennessee and running the score table for us, perfect job without a doubt. Everyone in the building had a ball, a lot of lifting and high energy, can't wait to do it again. Hope to see everyone soon.
